{
  "stem": "14552.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "23 Svoboda Ulice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-V-O-B-O-D-A",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "U-L-period.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Mukacevo.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was Kertvaros, which was the garden section of the town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kertvaros.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "K-E-R-T-V-A-R-O-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's an umlaut there someplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a three bedrooms which were-- which was for one of them doubled for a dining room, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had a-- a big dining room table, and it had a [NON-ENGLISH] here, and a [NON-ENGLISH] there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the kitchen had two tables in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One [NON-ENGLISH], one [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was a veranda which was also a succah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For the-- for the succah we opened up this ceiling, the attic.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we put on it at all kinds of decorations for succah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there a place in the summertime where we did the cooking and washing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In winter there was the laundry washing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And summertime summertime it was also as a kitchen to keep the upstairs cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we had a pantry where all the food was put away-- all the-- the fruits and vegetables.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And under the veranda we had a sand cellar where all the root vegetables were stored for the whole winter-- cabbage, and parsley, and parsnips, and carrots, and potatoes, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there was the cabbage, the barrel of cabbage which had-- which every one of these was a ritual.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "To put the cabbage away was a party.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "To flick the feathers was a party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was made into fun, because friends got together and, they were cleaning the cabbage.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then my father was planing the cabbage, and I was put in the barrel to stomp on the cabbage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were eating, and singing, and putting away food for the winter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the youngest, and I was pampered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was given-- I was given the-- the love that keeps me going.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
